{"tid":1064501,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「有圖」美女裸照，雙腿分開任睇！","createTime":"2019-03-16T15:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T15:29:57.000Z","uid":9769,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b145f7282a7e88f4f190378755549c82f5a1b14c","tid":1064501,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWcRqWy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbWcRqWy.png&h=f2d054d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64de2a0a20bf3482884e8a9577744f376cfaf6a2","tid":1064501,"uid":126529,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"你唔係睇細路女咩"},{"pid":"ddd51e6e48b0c1c925e58bc8576ba56c0079ddc9","tid":1064501,"uid":90820,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:28:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戀童監躉</span></span>"},{"pid":"e8e0f87e815ed17ec539cb4f0f4e56afe9eb2657","tid":1064501,"uid":90820,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"會員Agentcc原來係孌童犯，搞細路女坐監(1):<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/386856/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/386856/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n話說有位會員Agentcc因為分享佢坐監生活而出名<br />\n<br />\n佢仲成日出post炫耀北上叫雞<br />\n<br />\n深圳香格里拉田雞煲+蒸原隻大元貝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/385757/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/385757/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n個post入面佢貼左張單有佢個名：Tin siu hung <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/161125_88611fdb4f22c6ccbff9f4bc79f44c6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F161125_88611fdb4f22c6ccbff9f4bc79f44c6c.jpg&h=7fdcf59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打根據個名起底，原來條友唔係因為佢聲稱既經濟犯罪坐監，而係非禮好幾個未成年細路女既孌童風化犯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongcaselaw.com/category/tin-siu-hung-%E7%94%B0%E5%B0%91%E9%9B%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongcaselaw.com%2Fcategory%2Ftin-siu-hung-%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25B0%2591%25E9%259B%2584%2F&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=c3263f93\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongcaselaw.com/category/tin-siu-hung-%E7%94%B0%E5%B0%91%E9%9B%84/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20050528/4923942\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20050528%2F4923942&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=61cbba86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20050528%2F4923942&h=165a50b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20050528/4923942</a><br />\n<br />\n之前出post仲呃人話經濟犯罪，究竟佢講既野幾成真幾成假？<br />\n<br />\n(1)個post有唔少巴打起到新資料：<br />\n懷疑係Agentcc(田少雄)<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/180625_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F180625_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=79d7f01f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://get.google.com/albumarchive/110766364975201778040/album/AF1QipNRaaUDyAvx1dhEB7RgcRHo2o5m4Nk3IKkYaLUO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fget.google.com%2Falbumarchive%2F110766364975201778040%2Falbum%2FAF1QipNRaaUDyAvx1dhEB7RgcRHo2o5m4Nk3IKkYaLUO&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=233d87a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://get.google.com/albumarchive/110766364975201778040/album/AF1QipNRaaUDyAvx1dhEB7RgcRHo2o5m4Nk3IKkYaLUO</a><br />\n內有同細路女合照<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/195035_b8c5be7a33813027f06aa1a07842ed86.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F